To host the web application locally:
1. Repace 'YOUR_API_KEY' in app.py with your secret OpenAI's key.
2. Set up a virtual environment:
  2.1. In Windows Command Prompt, navigate to the chatbot directory.
  2.2. Create a new venv:
    python -m venv myenv
  2.3. Activate the virtual environment
    myenv\Scripts\activate
  2.4. Install required libraries (make sure you have pip installed with Python)
    pip install -r requirements.txt
  2.5. Start your web application:
    python app.py
  2.6 To exit:
    deactivate
